parsed.explanation: The XML string had several issues. The most important was that most special characters weren't escaped correctly which made it unreadable for parsers. Furthermore, the XML was not well formed as it was missing some start and end tags for the text surrounding the BIBL tag. Added a TEXT tag to encapsulate it. The '4tä' and '9.' have been corrected to '4to' and '9.' respectively, the 'Francken Genffer-Geld' Preis tag has been closed correctly, and the special characters have been replaced with their correct utf-8 representations.
